Hey, just saw your message about the get-together this weekend. We're definitely in. I think the best time would be around 4 on Saturday so we can catch up before dinner. Let me know if you need us to bring anything—we can swing by the store and grab snacks or whatever. Also, thanks for sending over those photos from the trip last month, they turned out great. The kids have been asking when we can go back to the beach. Anyway, let me know about Saturday. Hope everyone is doing well! Talk soon. Cheers, sounds like a plan. We can bring some music or games if the kids get bored. Looking forward to it.

Walmart

